---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" file="me.md" folder="about">
  <h1>JAMES<br/>RUNTAS</h1>

  <p>
    Hi — I'm a software developer based in <code>Ontario, CA</code>. I build
    things for the web, write about what I learn, and occasionally break things
    in interesting ways. <span class="cursor"></span>
  </p>

  <p>
    I care about clean code, good interfaces, and tools that make other
    developers' lives easier. Currently open to new opportunities.
  </p>

  <blockquote>
    "The best code is the code you don't have to write twice."
  </blockquote>

  <h2>// SKILLS</h2>
  <div class="skills-grid">
    <span class="skill">JavaScript</span>
    <span class="skill">TypeScript</span>
    <span class="skill">React</span>
    <span class="skill">Astro</span>
    <span class="skill">Node.js</span>
    <span class="skill">Python</span>
    <span class="skill">SQL</span>
    <span class="skill">Git</span>
    <span class="skill">CSS / Tailwind</span>
    <span class="skill">REST APIs</span>
  </div>

  <h2>// CURRENTLY</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Building projects and writing about them</li>
    <li>Open to full-time and contract roles</li>
    <li>Based in Ontario, Canada 🍁</li>
  </ul>
</Base>

<style>
  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 12px 0 24px;
    max-width: 680px;
  }
  .skill {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--teal);
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .skill::before {
    content: '● ';
    font-size: 7px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin-right: 4px;
  }
  .skill:hover { border-color: var(--teal); background: rgba(42,161,152,0.06); }
</style>
